content: tcm390: This month, tcm390 focused on delivering a series of fixes and enhancements to the elizaos/eliza repository, merging five pull requests. Their most impactful contribution was elizaos/eliza#6045, which exposed the state cache and fixed bootstrap types. They also supported the team by approving two other pull requests, with their overall work consisting of 17 commits primarily focused on bug fixes and other code improvements.
